io.vertx.up.commune.config

Class DictFabric

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.vertx.up.commune.exchange.DictFabric

  • public class DictFabric
extends Object

    DictFabric

    Combiner of Dict 1. ConcurrentMap<String, Epsilon> map stored field -> dict 2. ConcurrentMap<String, JsonArray> dictionary data in current channel 3. DualMapping Stored mapping ( from -> to ) 4. The fabric do not support mapping converting future( Important )
